# Web app for Writers
- Everything a writer needs to grow his carrear.
- We restore creative freedom and work alongside you to generate better results, with flexibility and you in control. The entire journey and experience, from ideation to sale, has been designed to guarantee the author's success.
- Integrated marketing and CRM. AI-powered data analysis and fundraising to expand your personal brand.

## Pages
- Onboarding: Creating an account is quick and easy.
- Profile: Set the public profile (marketplace)
- Dashboard: Main insights about their result
- Room: Show your books and book publishing journey.
- Analitics: Deep dive about book and readers.
- Settings: Configure their account, preferences, security and others stuffs.

## Open store
- Writers can create a public page to show his books and stats
- It's use to share in other social media and create authority.
- The reader can rent it there and be directed to read it in the app.
- The reader will also have the same view on their mobile phone (app), from the moment they are already reading a book or already have the app.